{"_id":"AbelTheYoungLove","name":"Abel the Young Lover - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"0150t4xm00muy1vv","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Abel the Young Lover","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young baker who has always been in \nlove with Bianca.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 112.","positive":"I am a young baker who has always been in \nlove with Bianca.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Abel the Young Lover","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart"},"sort":2700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628486,"modifiedTime":1781557628486,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AkimTheTamer19xx","name":"Akim the Tamer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00rp1sts00aog9hv","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Akim the Tamer","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a brave and skilled \ntamer. The tiger Tasha and the bear \nBerto are both dear to me, as they obey \nmy every command.</p>","notes":"In Your Eyes, with Your Feet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 158.","positive":"I am a brave and skilled \ntamer. The tiger Tasha and the bear \nBerto are both dear to me, as they obey \nmy every command.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Akim the Tamer","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet"},"sort":2000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637149,"modifiedTime":1781557637149,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AleksandrPtak05x","name":"Aleksandr Pták - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00p876ee017m21un","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Aleksandr Pták","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am divided between who I was before and \nthe spirit who took possession of my body. I have the urge to \nkill, but since my mind is clouded, I don’t always know why.\nSwallow’s</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 173.","positive":"I am divided between who I was before and \nthe spirit who took possession of my body. I have the urge to \nkill, but since my mind is clouded, I don’t always know why.\nSwallow’s","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Aleksandr Pták","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always"},"sort":600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637920,"modifiedTime":1781557637920,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AlexandraTheMoth","name":"Alexandra the Mother - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00gcx2ua00phf7et","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Alexandra the Mother","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a monster, deformed in body and mind. \nThe curse that keeps me alive means that I cannot forget \nwhat I have done. Now, with my misshapen mouth, I can \nonly grunt and whine, preventing me from imploring the \nforgiveness of my daughter.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 142.","positive":"I am a monster, deformed in body and mind. \nThe curse that keeps me alive means that I cannot forget \nwhat I have done. Now, with my misshapen mouth, I can \nonly grunt and whine, preventing me from imploring the \nforgiveness of my daughter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Alexandra the Mother","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet"},"sort":3300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636337,"modifiedTime":1781557636337,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AltheaTheAgentOf","name":"Althea the Agent of the Order - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"013c8o8i00cdyskv","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Althea the Agent of the Order","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Hunger Island","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a nun in the service of the Order and, \ndespite my ecclesiastical background, I have skills as a spy and \na fighter. The Order entrusts me with high-risk tasks because \nit has confidence in my unwavering faith and ruthlessness.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 99.","positive":"I am a nun in the service of the Order and, \ndespite my ecclesiastical background, I have skills as a spy and \na fighter. The Order entrusts me with high-risk tasks because \nit has confidence in my unwavering faith and ruthlessness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Althea the Agent of the Order","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Hunger Island"},"sort":1000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626372,"modifiedTime":1781557626372,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ArneTheCaptain06","name":"Arne the Captain - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01yryxwp0184ub5w","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Arne the Captain","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Hunger Island","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I once was a military man and I’ve earned the \ncrown’s respect. Now, as a ship’s captain, I serve my country and \nboast about my crew.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 95.","positive":"I once was a military man and I’ve earned the \ncrown’s respect. Now, as a ship’s captain, I serve my country and \nboast about my crew.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Arne the Captain","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Hunger Island"},"sort":700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626239,"modifiedTime":1781557626239,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
