{"_id":"BiancaKarenmann2","name":"Bianca Karenmann - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"000ie0uk009p1yyn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bianca Karenmann","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I’m a sweet young girl and I just want to live in \npeace. The power of the curse makes me strong and resilient. \nIt also gives me the power to make living beings explode from \nwithin.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 117.","positive":"I’m a sweet young girl and I just want to live in \npeace. The power of the curse makes me strong and resilient. \nIt also gives me the power to make living beings explode from \nwithin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bianca Karenmann","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart"},"sort":3000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628721,"modifiedTime":1781557628721,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BrunaThePoorWitc","name":"Bruna the Poor Witch - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00tx46z101wbz46m","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bruna the Poor Witch","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a poor old woman to whom life has \noffered only suffering. Sometimes I manifest strange powers, \nbut I have always concealed this ability out of fear of ending \nup at the stake.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 113.","positive":"I am a poor old woman to whom life has \noffered only suffering. Sometimes I manifest strange powers, \nbut I have always concealed this ability out of fear of ending \nup at the stake.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bruna the Poor Witch","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Bloodwhite's Heart"},"sort":400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628565,"modifiedTime":1781557628565,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CernobogPotmesil","name":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01qow4g800knt069","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>The rubies I received allowed me to recover \nfrom the fever that had plagued me and, thanks to them, I \nam now strong and healthy, but at what price? I feel anger \nand resentment towards those who live on the shoulders of \nthe poor people of Prague.</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 173.","positive":"The rubies I received allowed me to recover \nfrom the fever that had plagued me and, thanks to them, I \nam now strong and healthy, but at what price? I feel anger \nand resentment towards those who live on the shoulders of \nthe poor people of Prague.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always"},"sort":1700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637921,"modifiedTime":1781557637921,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
