{"_id":"JoannaCalledNana","name":"Joanna called Nana the Servant - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01fr0jum00yzu993","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Joanna called Nana the Servant","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I have been Lady Gwendolyn’s trusted personal \nservant for over ten years. I saw the young heir grow up and I \nam as fond of her as if she were my own daughter.</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 84.","positive":"I have been Lady Gwendolyn’s trusted personal \nservant for over ten years. I saw the young heir grow up and I \nam as fond of her as if she were my own daughter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Joanna called Nana the Servant","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe"},"sort":5200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625638,"modifiedTime":1781557625638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
