{"_id":"KonstantinSvobod","name":"Konstantin Svoboda the Alchemist - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01xttdkv01s8r6no","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Konstantin Svoboda the Alchemist","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am one of the most prominent alchemists in \nPrague. My brilliant experiments could easily backfire on me.</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 167.","positive":"I am one of the most prominent alchemists in \nPrague. My brilliant experiments could easily backfire on me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Konstantin Svoboda the Alchemist","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always"},"sort":4000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637513,"modifiedTime":1781557637513,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Lisbet17xxxxxxxx","name":"Lisbet - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00165aff00q0s23g","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lisbet","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young widow and I settled in the village \nto start anew. I have experienced many misfortunes in my life, \nwhich have forced me to become stubborn and strong-willed. \nHowever, I’ve managed to stay kind and generous.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 143.","positive":"I am a young widow and I settled in the village \nto start anew. I have experienced many misfortunes in my life, \nwhich have forced me to become stubborn and strong-willed. \nHowever, I’ve managed to stay kind and generous.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lisbet","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet"},"sort":1800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636357,"modifiedTime":1781557636357,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MercenaryAndRese","name":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"005odbvm005o1s15","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled adventurer and treasure hunter, \nand I have no qualms about doing what it takes to get what \nI want.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 139.","positive":"I am a skilled adventurer and treasure hunter, \nand I have no qualms about doing what it takes to get what \nI want.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, Stegeborg's Quiet"},"sort":800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636228,"modifiedTime":1781557636228,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MtyryaTheFairyAl","name":"Mtyrya the Fairy also called the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00ldkllq00d3ivxf","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Mtyrya the Fairy also called the Cauldron Fae","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an ancient fairy bound to nature. I hate humans and modernity. Thanks \nto my power, anything others believe to be impossible, I can make possible.</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 85.","positive":"I am an ancient fairy bound to nature. I hate humans and modernity. Thanks \nto my power, anything others believe to be impossible, I can make possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Mtyrya the Fairy also called the Cauldron Fae","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe"},"sort":3600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625700,"modifiedTime":1781557625700,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NatureRisesUp13x","name":"Nature Rises Up - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"00z2licu0182o1dp","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nature Rises Up","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>Navigating inside the lair without the consent of the Cauldron Fae \nexposes the intruders to the ire of the many plants. Ivy tentacles and pollen mists rise to \nblock those who walk without their lady’s approval.\nMtyrya the Fairy also called the \nCauldron Fae</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 85.","positive":"Navigating inside the lair without the consent of the Cauldron Fae \nexposes the intruders to the ire of the many plants. Ivy tentacles and pollen mists rise to \nblock those who walk without their lady’s approval.\nMtyrya the Fairy also called the \nCauldron Fae","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nature Rises Up","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe"},"sort":1400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625700,"modifiedTime":1781557625700,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"OstromirMaly12xx","name":"Ostromir Malý - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01o1o0ob01lxlgfw","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Ostromir Malý","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I rule Prague on behalf of Empress Maria \nTheresa and, after the failed siege, I hold the city’s fate in the \npalm of my hand. The recent murders are complicating my \nlife, though so far the noble families support my authority.</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 166.","positive":"I rule Prague on behalf of Empress Maria \nTheresa and, after the failed siege, I hold the city’s fate in the \npalm of my hand. The recent murders are complicating my \nlife, though so far the noble families support my authority.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Ostromir Malý","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Will Stay with You Always"},"sort":1300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637466,"modifiedTime":1781557637466,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
