{"_id":"Pietrik34xxxxxxx","name":"Pietrik - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01a64tqg008hcddh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietrik","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young rebel and I fight the creeping industrialization of London with \nall my strength.</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 87.","positive":"I am a young rebel and I fight the creeping industrialization of London with \nall my strength.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietrik","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, I Don't Believe"},"sort":3500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625744,"modifiedTime":1781557625744,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PietroGonsalvaRe","name":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"001h4kup01xppklk","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, The House of Roses","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a rich and powerful nobleman, and I have \nmanaged to ingratiate myself with the Papal State. I love being \nin charge, but over time I’ve learned to trust those who are more \nexperienced than I am.</p>","notes":"The House of Roses - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 125.","positive":"I am a rich and powerful nobleman, and I have \nmanaged to ingratiate myself with the Papal State. I love being \nin charge, but over time I’ve learned to trust those who are more \nexperienced than I am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, The House of Roses"},"sort":1600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557629741,"modifiedTime":1781557629741,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PrincescaOfVigo3","name":"Princesca of Vigo - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":"0084tmes01vsqp2t","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princesca of Vigo","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors","source":"The Broken Ones, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am Cinder and, thanks to \nmagic, I pretend to be the attractive and kind \nPrincesca. Thanks to the power of the Kind \nMother, I control the entire city. I am cold and \ndetermined and I won’t let anyone stand in \nmy way.</p>","notes":"In Your Eyes, with Your Feet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 154.","positive":"I am Cinder and, thanks to \nmagic, I pretend to be the attractive and kind \nPrincesca. Thanks to the power of the Kind \nMother, I control the entire city. I am cold and \ndetermined and I won’t let anyone stand in \nmy way.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Princesca of Vigo","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet, In Your Eyes, with Your Feet"},"sort":3900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636919,"modifiedTime":1781557636919,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
